<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f0f2f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .blog-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .blog-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
        }

        .blog-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .blog-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .blog-meta {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .blog-content {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Fade in animation */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="blog-container">
        <div class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-title">10 Tips for Healthy Living</div>
            <div class="blog-meta">By John Doe | Aug 21, 2025</div>
            <div class="blog-content">
                Living a healthy life doesnâ€™t have to be complicated. Focus on eating fresh fruits and vegetables, staying hydrated, exercising regularly, and getting enough sleep.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-title">The Benefits of Meditation</div>
            <div class="blog-meta">By Jane Smith | Aug 20, 2025</div>
            <div class="blog-content">
                Meditation can reduce stress, improve focus, and boost mental health. Spending just 10 minutes a day practicing mindfulness can make a big difference.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-title">Exploring Nature: Hiking Tips</div>
            <div class="blog-meta">By Mike Johnson | Aug 18, 2025</div>
            <div class="blog-content">
                Hiking is a great way to stay fit and enjoy the outdoors. Always carry water, wear comfortable shoes, and respect nature while exploring trails.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
